# POLYMORPHISM
          Çok-Biçimlilik


          Animals          speak()      w Loud / Normal / Low 
                                        -------------------
                                        voice

                              inheritance
          -------------------------------------------------
          Main     Sub          Sub          Sub
          Class    Class        Class        Class
          -------  ----------   -----------  ------------
          Animals: dog.speak(), cat.speak(), bird.speak()     
          Voice:   loud.speak(), normal.speak(), low.speak()


	A man can have many roles like actor, doctor, astronaut and so on. same person can have different roles.


